name.description: Name of the filter field. Valid values can be found in the EC2 [`DescribeNetworkInsightsAnalyses`](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSEC2/latest/APIReference/API_DescribeNetworkInsightsAnalyses.html) API Reference.

values.description: Set of values that are accepted for the given filter field. Results will be selected if any given value matches.
